AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000502> "A two-dimensional data item is a representation or analysis, commonly applied in studying planar material properties or surface phenomena."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000502> "true"^^xsd:boolean)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000502> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000027>)

