AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000036> "Lattice centering value is a categorical value specification which describes th geometric arrangement of lattice points in a unit cell with one of the values: primitive, body centered, face centered, base centered."@en)
EquivalentClasses(<https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000036> ObjectOneOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000043> <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000044> <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000045> <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000046>))
