AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/noes/NOES_0000036> "Normal direction is a rolled sheet direction which is normal to the rolling plane of the sheet."@en)
EquivalentClasses(<https://w3id.org/pmd/noes/NOES_0000036> ObjectIntersectionOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/noes/NOES_0000001> ObjectHasValue(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000077> <https://w3id.org/pmd/noes/NOES_0000030>)))
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/noes/NOES_0000036> <https://w3id.org/pmd/noes/NOES_0000001>)
