AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/noes/NOES_0000070> "Magnetic field strength is a process attribute of an aplication of magnetic field process which characterizes the magnitude the external / applied magnetic field."@en)
