# Individual: <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000043> (primitive)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000043> "primitive"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000043> "P")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000043> "Primitive centering type is a centering type, where lattice points are located only on the corners of a unit cell, i.e., at coordinates (0,0,0)."@en)

# Individual: <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000044> (body centered)

